        <mxCell id="gqyGLWo6HeyIAnXtJu5Z-117" parent="1" style="shape=callout;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;perimeter=calloutPerimeter;fillColor=#e51400;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#B20000;" value="&lt;div&gt;still there&#39;s another code smell which called primitive obsession&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;that&#39;s when you use strings and numbers to represent a concept&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;and we&#39;re passing dictionary of string:string&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;but analytics can &amp;nbsp;be prices or dates ...&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
